// Reference: Nishita 1993, Preetham 1999, Hillaire 2020 (simplified).\r
//\r
// World units are metres.  The ground sits at y ≈ 0 so the camera is placed at\r
// (0, R_E + cameraPos.y, 0) in atmosphere space.\r
